						               													<description>On the Giza plateau the best architects of Ancient Egypt are called to imprint the mark of the Pharaoh. It's not just a matter of building tombs, but of erecting actual engineering masterpieces, monuments that will be worshipped and that will forever raise the honor of the Pharaoh to heaven.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The competition among architects is a snake hiding in the sand ready to attack; building projects and workers management mingle with the worship of the gods. Wisely choosing which god to ask for blessing will be crucial for our Fame to outshine all the others&amp;rsquo; one, ensuring the immortality of our name. Let&amp;rsquo;s hold tight our precious Scarab and with the power it infuses us, we are ready to make Egypt the most incredible place in the world&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A game of dice and card combos that makes timing and control of the opponents&amp;rsquo; strategies a core element. Fast and deep, Pyramidice boasts a very high replayability and different strategic paths to pursue victory. A game that easily introduces new players to the world of boardgames and wisely keeps experienced players in suspense until the very end.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
